  {
    "hotel_id": "5466343",
    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/the-cube-hotel/hotel/seoul-kr.html",
    "name": "The Cube Hotel",
    "detail": "The Cube felt like a little, cozy home in the heart of Myeong-dong. It’s a four-ish minute walk from the station, up a slight incline, and up a few flights of stairs. The hosts were extremely friendly, informative, and kind. The facilities were immaculate and easy-to-use. The beds were clean, and they provide a small locker with two towels and a pair of slippers waiting for you inside of it. A nice breakfast was offered each morning, and they have water and tea to consume all throughout the day. The other guests were respectful and quiet, and I felt very safe staying there. Whilst I stayed, they offered a rooftop BBQ event under the full moon for a small cover fee. I couldn’t go, but I’m sure it was amazing!! The host gave me a cool, unique Seoul keychain souvenir made from his lobby’s 3D printer, and for checking out they gave me gummy bears as a thank you for staying with them. When I return to Seoul, I would stay with them again! 💗 ",
    "area": "Myeong-dong,Seoul - View on map",
    "rating": "8.4",
